summary: A highly motivated individual fluent in written and spoken Dutch, English, French and German, with experience in freelance writing, PR services, marketing and promotions, having taken on more technical roles in engineering, IT consultancy and data management as well. I’m a Full Sail University alumnus, seeking a challenging venture in marketing, advertising and PR, which draws on my strengths in writing and communication, brand development and placement, creative problem solving, time management, collecting and summarizing data, and content creation and management. I have a good working knowledge of many industry leading software applications and am comfortable working under time pressure and presenting myself in a professional manner with excellent inter-personal communication and social skills. I work to the highest standard with an eye for detail, originality and quality whilst successfully meeting deadlines.
